 name←{opts}CaseCode name;opts
 ⍝ Case-code a file name located
 :If U.debug=2
     (1+⊃⎕LC)⎕STOP⊃⎕SI
 :EndIf
 :Trap DEBUG↓0
     :If 900⌶⍬  ⍝ only expert users provide correct link options to avoid lookup
     :AndIf 0∊⍴opts←U.LookupFile name
         U.Error'Not linked: ',⍕name
     :EndIf     
     name←opts.dir U.CaseCode opts.flatten⊢name
 :Else
     U.Resignal 1
 :EndTrap
